// Memory & Preferences (Giving Bots “Memory”)

Scripts don’t actually remember like humans and cannot access Chat Memory or the API prompt. Each new message starts fresh. But we can **simulate memory** by writing details into the scenario or personality. The model will read these fields and act as if it remembers.

